OL IV: At 2100 trees, maximum daily fruit is 2730.
OL V: At 3100 trees, maximum daily fruit is 4030.
OA I: At 3500 trees, maximum daily fruit is 4550.
OA II: At 5,000 trees, maximum daily fruit is 6,500.[/list][/s][line]
